name: FDS Civilian Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct civilian FDS ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs.

name: FDS Military Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct FDS military ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs.

name: FDS Weapons Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct a range of basic FDS weaponry.

name: FDS Advanced Weapons Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct a range of advanced FDS weaponry.

name: FDS Missile Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct a range of FDS missile weapons.
